    "title": "Whenever I'm caught between two evils, I take the one I've never tried.",
    "description": "While held, it grants life steal from all damage you deal. Its projectiles also explode on impact for splash damage, and that splash scales with grenade damage bonuses. It also carries a small critical-hit bonus."
  },
  "notes": "Rubi shots detonate on impact, and the splash portion is boosted by grenade damage bonuses. Axton does not receive healing from Sabre Turret damage. Damaging health-bar objects such as barrels or fuse boxes will also trigger healing. Self-damage can still heal you if the hit is fully absorbed by shields; if it reaches health, the life steal may only offset part of the damage.",
